org.jamesframework.core.search.algo.exh

Interface SolutionIterator<SolutionType extends Solution>

  • Type Parameters:
    SolutionType - solution type of generated solutions, required to extends Solution
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SubsetSolutionIterator

    public interface SolutionIterator<SolutionType extends Solution>
    Interface of a generic solution iterator that iterates through a collection of solutions. The exhaustive search algorithm depends on solution iterators to evaluate all possible solutions. To use this algorithm for a specific problem, a solution iterator has to be created first, which traverses the entire solution space corresponding to this problem.
    Author:
    Herman De Beukelaer
